Zombie Survival is simple shooter game written in C#.
It has been created as a credit project for a
course Advanced programming in .NET in Mathematics and Physics faculty, Charles University.
Goal of the game is to kill as many zombies as possible and
survive for the longest period. You can control player's movements
by A, W, S, D keys, you aim at zombies with mouse cursor, shoot
them with left mouse button and change guns with mouse wheel.